dfischer.utils

Class SymmetricEncryptURLConnection

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.net.URLConnection
      • dfischer.utils.SymmetricEncryptURLConnection

  • public class SymmetricEncryptURLConnection
extends java.net.URLConnection
    A special URL connection class that supports the URL protocol named "encrypted:" used to load encrypted jar files when executing a load test and decrypt and define the jar files on the fly by using a symmetric key.
    Since:
    V5.4-K
    See Also:
    LoadtestPluginClassLoader, SymmetricEncryptURLStreamHandlerFactory, SymmetricEncryptURLStreamHandler, SymmetricEncrypt
